<br />Thanks Tepples, I'll look over those documents. 
<br />
<br />Off hand, do you know a way to modify an NES to run these carts? Does disabling the lockout chip on the NES mainboard allow for using Famicombox games, or do they need a handshake signal from the hardware before they execute?
<br />
<br />My main NES I already have modified by both disabling the lockout chip and by performing the PowerPak FDS sound modification, so if that is all I require, then that's perfect. 
<br />
<br />-Xious

		

